        protected void findSecurityInstanceId​(org.eclipse.leshan.core.link.Link[] objectLinks,
                                      java.lang.String endpoint)
        "Short Server ID": This Resource MUST be set when the Bootstrap-Server Resource has a value of 'false'. The values ID:0 and ID:65535 values MUST NOT be used for identifying the LwM2M Server. "Short Server ID": - Link Instance (lwm2m Server) hase linkParams with key = "ssid" value = "shortId" (ver lvm2m = 1.1). - Link Instance (bootstrap Server) hase not linkParams with key = "ssid" (ver lvm2m = 1.1).
